extendedInfo.description: If you are Rick Ross's fan, this app is right for you. Whenever you want to check Rick Ross's lyrics, just open this app and choose the lyrics that you want. You don't have to access the internet to get the lyrics. We provide all Rick Ross's lyrics here. In the Album tab, you can choose lyrics based on the album. In All lyrics tab, all of Rick Ross's lyrics are here. You can quickly search the lyrics by using the search bar at the top of the page.Hope you guy enjoy using this app as much as I enjoy developing it. :)-------------------------------- Main Features -------------------------------- - Lyrics categorized by album - Show all lyrics - Search lyrics-------------------------------- List of albums -------------------------------- - Port of Miami- Trilla- Deeper Than Rap- Teflon Don- God Forgives, I Don't-------------------------------- List of lyrics -------------------------------- - 911- 10 Bricks- 100 Black Coffins- 3 Kings- 9 Piece- 9 Piece (Remix)- All I Have In This World (Japanese Denim)- All I Really Want- All The Money In The World- Amsterdam- Ashamed- Ashes To Ashes- Aston Martin Music- Audio Meth- B.M.F.
